########################
# Notes
########################
# âœ… Keep these files in VCS:
# - `composer.json`, `composer.lock` (lockfile is useful in many projects)
# - `package.json`, `yarn.lock` / `pnpm-lock.yaml` if relevant
# - migration files and canonical DB schema (`database/migrations/`, `database/ecommerce_db.sql`)
# - application source under `app/`, `config/`, `resources/`, `routes/`, etc.

# If you need to force-add a file that matches an ignore rule, use:
#   git add -f <file>

# Custom local ignores can be added to .git/info/exclude (not committed) or to global gitignore
# (see `git config --global core.excludesfile`).
